to those with an aug birthday what do you love most about your life and what do you give thanks to most so happy birthday the reason i ask this is because today is my mom's th b day and she has advanced stage cancer she was diagnosed june of last year at which time the doctors said that my mom had a year survival chance of less than weeks she spent in the hospital including her th b day where she told me that she would probably never see it is now a year later and although she is still receiving chemo and sometimes feels like garbage her spirits are up she has lived half a century and although i don't know billions of people i feel she is one of the sweetest appreciative and most humble person i have ever met despite the suffering and loss she has experienced in her life i just wanted to ask those with b days today what do you love and appreciate most about your years here bless you for being so nice about your mum she 's a wonderful brave woman by the sound of her i hope she is going to win her battle and manage a few more birthdays to share with you a very good friend just mailed this q to me as it's my birthday too i've had more than your mum though i understand this dreadful illness must be very upsetting for you as well as your mum my own mother died of cancer when she was just my son died not of cancer nearly five years ago he was so what i appreciate most is the family and friends that are still here it feels like a very unkind world some days but i have learnt to laugh again it's wonderful to see a sunny day my husbands head is still on the pillow when i wake each morning i have my happy memories firmly tucked in this older head of mine and i try to lose the sad ones what i would like to say though is the gift of a child is the most important thing in the whole world so remember to tell your mum you love her every day and when you have to leave her at bedtime always say i'll see you tomorrow then she will believe she always has tomorrow to look forward to ho